在i和j循环上应用分块，以提升缓存局部性。将内层循环分割成适合L1/L2缓存大小的块。

```cpp
int tile_size = 32; // 根据实际缓存大小调整
for (t = 0; t <= _PB_TSTEPS - 1; t++) {
    for (ii = 1; ii <= _PB_N - 2; ii += tile_size) {
        for (jj = 1; jj <= _PB_N - 2; jj += tile_size) {
            for (i = ii; i <= min(ii + tile_size - 1, _PB_N - 2); i++) {
                for (j = jj; j <= min(jj + tile_size - 1, _PB_N - 2); j++) {
                    A[i][j] = (A[i-1][j-1] + A[i-1][j] + A[i-1][j+1]
                               + A[i][j-1] + A[i][j] + A[i][j+1]
                               + A[i+1][j-1] + A[i+1][j] + A[i+1][j+1])/SCALAR_VAL(9.0);
                }
            }
        }
    }
}
```

